Exactly!

338
00:17:08,950 --> 00:17:09,950
You can't wrong the innocent.

339
00:17:09,950 --> 00:17:10,830
Punish the real criminal!

340
00:17:12,350 --> 00:17:13,000
Your Honor!

341
