390
00:18:49,710 --> 00:18:51,000
Guards, seize him!

391
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:52,430
Magistrate Meng!

392
00:18:52,430 --> 00:18:52,920
We had an agreement!

393
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:53,350
Silence!

394
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:54,310
You can't do this, Magistrate Meng!

395
00:18:54,310 --> 00:18:55,400
We had a deal!

396
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,350
Magistrate Meng!

397
00:18:59,190 --> 00:19:00,160
