406
00:19:20,950 --> 00:19:21,760
Magistrate Meng!

407
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:26,950
Magistrate Meng, you are indeed perceptive and just!

408
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,430
When word of this spreads,

409
00:19:28,430 --> 00:19:30,760
it will surely become a celebrated tale!

410
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:32,110
A celebrated tale indeed!

411
00:19:32,800 --> 00:19:34,400
If my father hears

412
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:36,040
about today's case,

413
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,950
he will surely praise Magistrate Meng

414
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,560
for handling it so brilliantly!

415
00:19:39,560 --> 00:19:40,760
So brilliantly!

416
00:19:42,520 --> 00:19:44,430
Sir, the people's trust is crucial.

417
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:49,000
Considering

418
00:19:49,110 --> 00:19:51,520
that Ms. Ji's urgency to save her mother

419
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:52,920
and the circumstances,

420
00:19:53,350 --> 00:19:55,310
this court will not pursue the matter

421
00:19:55,760 --> 00:19:57,160
