Yingying.

431
00:20:59,110 --> 00:20:59,920
Mother.

432
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,430
Let's go home.

433
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:04,950
Let's go home.

434
00:21:21,760 --> 00:21:22,560
Yingying,

435
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:25,760
