440
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:43,160
to save me?

441
00:21:43,520 --> 00:21:44,430
No, Mother.

442
00:21:44,950 --> 00:21:46,800
It was my own decision to marry him.

443
00:21:47,710 --> 00:21:48,470
No.

444
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:49,800
That can't be.

445
00:21:50,520 --> 00:21:52,040
You're lying to me.

446
00:21:53,110 --> 00:21:54,760
