449
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:05,280
Yingying,

450
00:22:05,590 --> 00:22:06,920
I'm sorry.

451
00:22:07,760 --> 00:22:09,230
It's my fault for dragging you down.

452
00:22:09,230 --> 00:22:11,430
Mother, don't say that.

453
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:14,160
Although marrying into the Yang family

454
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:16,350
was a matter of necessity,

455
00:22:17,430 --> 00:22:19,350
I've long admired Yang Jinglan.

456
00:22:20,350 --> 00:22:21,760
Though it was by chance,

457
00:22:22,520 --> 00:22:24,040
I am willing.

458
00:22:25,950 --> 00:22:26,760
Really?

459
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:28,310
Yes.

460
00:22:33,230 --> 00:22:34,040
Before,

461
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:37,110
I only wanted to keep you away from trouble.

462
00:22:37,830 --> 00:22:40,350
At that time, Yang Jinglan was also burdened with problems.

463
00:22:41,040 --> 00:22:43,590
I truly didn't want to marry you off to him.

464
00:22:45,520 --> 00:22:46,760
But who could have guessed

465
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:48,560
