467
00:22:51,230 --> 00:22:52,230
Did Yang Jinglan

468
00:22:52,470 --> 00:22:54,190
want to marry me from the start?

469
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:55,560
Silly child,

470
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:57,950
can't you see his feelings for you?

471
00:22:58,430 --> 00:22:59,710
Has he not treated you well?

472
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:02,640
He treats me very well.

473
00:23:02,710 --> 00:23:03,920
He always has.

474
00:23:05,190 --> 00:23:05,920
It's just

475
00:23:06,280 --> 00:23:08,160
that we've always referred to each other as allies,

476
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:10,160
never expressing our true feelings.

477
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:14,230
I had planned to ask him directly

478
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:15,920
when he returned.

479
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:19,230
A few days ago,

480
00:23:19,430 --> 00:23:22,190
