490
00:23:46,950 --> 00:23:48,760
have become so hard to put into words.

491
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:53,110
I'm happy for you.

492
00:23:55,430 --> 00:23:56,160
There's no rush.

493
00:23:56,710 --> 00:23:57,640
No rush at all.

494
00:23:58,710 --> 00:23:59,880
As long as your hearts

495
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:01,160
are connected,

496
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:03,070
I believe some words

497
00:24:03,590 --> 00:24:05,190
can still be understood

498
00:24:05,560 --> 00:24:07,350
even if they're left unsaid.

499
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:10,760
He and I

500
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,400
have a lifetime ahead of us.

501
00:24:17,760 --> 00:24:18,590
Mother,

502
00:24:18,830 --> 00:24:19,800
it's time for your medicine.

503
00:24:32,110 --> 00:24:32,920
Mother,

504
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:35,160
once you've recovered,

505
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:37,350
we'll leave Yizhou

506
00:24:37,590 --> 00:24:38,830
and move to Jiangnan.

507
00:24:39,350 --> 00:24:42,000
We'll live a peaceful life as a family.

508
00:24:42,520 --> 00:24:43,800
You and Yaoting go first.

509
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,160
I'll join you after I settle things here.

510
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:54,520
If you come with us to Jiangnan,

511
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:56,190
