512
00:24:56,710 --> 00:24:57,760
What about the Yang family?

513
00:24:58,950 --> 00:25:01,430
The Yang family's business will expand to Jiangnan too.

514
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:03,560
I'll manage it then.

515
00:25:04,430 --> 00:25:06,920
And after this year, Yang Jinglan can transfer his post.

516
00:25:07,110 --> 00:25:08,400
He'll come with me.

517
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:09,830
Yingying,

518
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,350
