542
00:26:28,310 --> 00:26:29,110
I don't know.

543
00:26:32,590 --> 00:26:34,350
What does she love to play with?

544
00:26:34,350 --> 00:26:35,310
When she's upset,

545
00:26:35,310 --> 00:26:37,070
what does she like to do the most?

546
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,710
I don't know.

547
00:26:52,310 --> 00:26:53,230
Yaoting!

548
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:56,710
