573
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:46,760
All right.

574
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:49,190
Let me help you put it on.

575
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:53,160
Thank you, Mother.

576
00:27:55,280 --> 00:27:57,040
So, what do you truly understand?

577
00:28:01,830 --> 00:28:04,040
I know that since I've married her,

578
00:28:05,280 --> 00:28:06,880
I must be her support,

579
00:28:07,710 --> 00:28:09,470
so she won't face the hardships alone.

580
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:14,710
You and she are like-minded,

581
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:16,160
with hearts that resonate.

582
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:18,040
But marriage

583
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:19,070
is more than just that.

584
00:28:19,950 --> 00:28:21,070
For a husband and wife,

585
00:28:21,470 --> 00:28:22,160
the various household affairs

586
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:22,880
of daily life

587
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,280
can wear down feelings

588
00:28:24,520 --> 00:28:26,520
just as much as external hardships.

589
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:29,920
And Yingying is no ordinary woman.

590
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:31,350
Perhaps,

591
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:34,760
it will be even harder for her to adjust.

592
00:28:39,950 --> 00:28:40,760
That's true,

593
00:28:43,560 --> 00:28:44,640
but where she belongs

594
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,280
is by my side,

595
00:28:47,070 --> 00:28:48,880
not with the prominent Yang family.

596
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:51,110
Once she fulfills her obligations to the Yang family,

597
00:28:51,470 --> 00:28:52,680
we'll move out.

598
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:54,680
Through every meal and every night,

599
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,680
through every season,

600
00:28:57,520 --> 00:28:58,560
I'll be with her,

601
00:28:58,880 --> 00:28:59,710
love her,

602
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:00,800
understand her,

603
00:29:01,230 --> 00:29:02,070
and respect her.

604
00:29:03,310 --> 00:29:04,830
Even though she's now my wife,

605
00:29:05,760 --> 00:29:06,430
Ji Yingying

606
00:29:06,760 --> 00:29:08,160
is still herself first

607
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:10,070
before she is my wife.

608
00:29:41,070 --> 00:29:41,920
Yang Jinglan,

609
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:43,520
who allowed you to come out?

610
00:29:53,650 --> 00:29:55,620
[To Ms. Yang: I am Dr. Zhang. Based on my evaluation,]

611
00:29:55,650 --> 00:29:57,630
[Mr. Yang's condition allows him to travel by carriage.]

612
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,880
Did you force him

613
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:02,880
to write this?

614
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:05,110
In your eyes,

615
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:07,280
am I truly so unrefined?

616
00:30:10,470 --> 00:30:11,280
Come on,

617
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:12,310
help me up.

618
00:30:18,470 --> 00:30:19,430
What are you trying to do?

619
00:30:19,430 --> 00:30:20,280
Don't move.

620
00:30:20,950 --> 00:30:21,880
It's my first time visiting.

621
00:30:22,110 --> 00:30:24,040
I must pay my respects to my mother-in-law.

622
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:31,070
Come on, Yingying,

623
00:30:32,070 --> 00:30:32,880
help me up.

624
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:34,430
But you...

625
00:30:36,830 --> 00:30:37,640
Please, I'm begging you.

626
00:30:43,830 --> 00:30:44,430
Take care.

627
00:30:45,520 --> 00:30:46,110
As you wish.

628
00:31:02,830 --> 00:31:03,830
Guo Kui,

629
00:31:04,230 --> 00:31:04,950
look at me.

630
00:31:05,520 --> 00:31:08,070
I've finally entered through the front door

631
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:09,830
with proper dignity.

632
00:31:10,230 --> 00:31:11,040
Shut up.

633
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:14,280
Mother.

634
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:19,280
Mr. Yang, you're still injured.

635
00:31:19,520 --> 00:31:20,470
No need for formalities.

636
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:21,950
Etiquette cannot be abandoned.

637
00:31:28,280 --> 00:31:30,560
I hereby pay my respects to you.

638
00:31:38,070 --> 00:31:38,920
The marriage was rushed,

639
00:31:39,470 --> 00:31:41,070
and I couldn't inform you in time.

640
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:42,880
Please forgive me.

641
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:50,680
Good child, get up.

642
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:58,520
Before, I was so worried about Yingying's safety

643
00:31:58,950 --> 00:32:00,680
that I nearly ruined your union.

644
00:32:01,710 --> 00:32:03,280
Now that you're finally together,

645
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:05,160
I've come to understand.

646
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:08,430
From now on, our family will stand together

647
00:32:08,430 --> 00:32:09,520
through thick and thin.

648
00:32:11,520 --> 00:32:12,920
I entrust our Yingying

649
00:32:14,110 --> 00:32:15,280
to your care.

650
00:32:22,280 --> 00:32:23,230
Please don't worry.

651
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:25,880
As long as I'm by Yingying's side,

652
00:32:26,560 --> 00:32:27,640
I'll protect her

653
00:32:29,110 --> 00:32:29,920
until she...

654
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:32,710
No,

655
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:35,760
until I give my last breath.

656
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:47,040
The Crown Prince sends congratulations to the Ji family!

657
00:33:04,470 --> 00:33:05,280
Mrs. Ji,

658
00:33:06,280 --> 00:33:07,230
His Highness congratulates

659
00:33:07,680 --> 00:33:09,880
Inspector Yang and Ms. Ji on their joyous union

660
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:11,160
and sends these gifts

661
00:33:11,310 --> 00:33:12,470
to celebrate the occasion.

662
00:33:26,350 --> 00:33:29,880
The entire Ji family bows in gratitude for His Highness's generosity.

663
00:33:38,470 --> 00:33:39,310
Please, rise.

664
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:52,640
This is a gift

665
00:33:53,280 --> 00:33:54,470
that my senior prepared for me.

666
00:33:55,040 --> 00:33:57,160
Please accept it, Mrs. Ji.

667
00:33:58,310 --> 00:34:00,280
The Crown Prince has prepared so much already.

668
00:34:01,830 --> 00:34:03,040
Your husband

669
00:34:03,040 --> 00:34:04,760
is using the Crown Prince's name

670
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:06,070
to make up your betrothal gifts.

671
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:08,670
Now let's see

672
00:34:08,670 --> 00:34:11,470
who dares say your marriage isn't proper anymore!

673
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:16,950
Though I stole you as my wife,

674
00:34:17,710 --> 00:34:18,950
what other wives have,

675
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,390
my wife

676
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:21,560
will have as well.

677
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:24,190
I'll make sure you get

678
00:34:24,630 --> 00:34:26,390
everything you deserve.

679
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:47,630
Slow down.

680
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:50,840
Here.

681
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:51,190
They're still so careless.

682
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:30,280
My mother and brother insisted

683
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:31,630
that I bring these small items.

684
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:33,800
They're just everyday things I use.

685
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:35,600
They're afraid I'm not used to the Yang family.

686
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:41,040
If you ever need anything else,

687
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:42,080
just let me know.

688
00:36:42,870 --> 00:36:44,390
I'll have someone get it for you.

689
00:37:01,470 --> 00:37:02,230
I don't need it.

690
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,320
Could you go slower?

691
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:14,230
Yang Jinglan.

692
00:37:14,910 --> 00:37:15,840
Fine.

693
00:37:31,040 --> 00:37:32,600
Why are you staring at me?

694
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,120
Because you're beautiful.

695
00:38:01,080 --> 00:38:03,040
Yang Jinglan, can you say something?

696
00:38:03,630 --> 00:38:04,800
It's too quiet.

697
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:07,800
All right.

698
00:38:08,840 --> 00:38:10,080
Why don't you ask me

699
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:12,080
about me and the Crown Prince?

700
00:38:13,430 --> 00:38:14,280
Fine!

701
00:38:15,710 --> 00:38:17,360
You're an inspector

702
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:18,630
and carry the Crown Prince's orders.

703
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:20,320
So, you're one of his men?

704
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:22,710
More or less.

705
00:38:23,670 --> 00:38:25,120
What do you mean by "more or less"?

706
00:38:34,120 --> 00:38:36,000
You dare to eat my chicken?

707
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:40,080
That'll be 500 taels. Cash only.

708
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:42,600
A guest is always welcome.

709
00:38:42,910 --> 00:38:44,000
Don't be so stingy.

710
00:38:46,710 --> 00:38:48,080
Aren't you curious

711
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:49,910
about who I am?

712
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:53,080
Looking at your attire,

713
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:54,320
you're either rich or noble.

714
00:38:55,230 --> 00:38:56,150
No ordinary person would come

715
00:38:56,150 --> 00:38:57,600
to such a godforsaken place.

716
00:38:58,190 --> 00:38:59,910
You must be following orders from that old man.

717
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:01,080
Do you know

718
00:39:01,710 --> 00:39:03,080
that the old man you speak of

719
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:05,800
was once the Crown Prince's tutor?

720
00:39:06,080 --> 00:39:07,080
I didn't know before.

721
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:08,190
Now I do.

722
00:39:09,230 --> 00:39:11,390
Turns out I'm not the only person that the old man's messed with.

723
00:39:12,630 --> 00:39:13,710
If you lie with coal, you get blackened.

724
00:39:14,040 --> 00:39:15,600
The Crown Prince must be terribly crooked, then.

725
00:39:16,630 --> 00:39:17,430
Who is it?

726
00:39:20,630 --> 00:39:21,430
Greetings, Sir.

727
00:39:23,040 --> 00:39:23,870
He's your teacher?

728
00:39:24,630 --> 00:39:26,840
Old man, how many students have you taken in?

729
00:39:27,080 --> 00:39:27,870
In my entire life,

730
00:39:27,870 --> 00:39:29,520
I've only taken you two as disciples.

731
00:39:30,040 --> 00:39:31,430
Especially you, little rascal,

732
00:39:31,430 --> 00:39:32,710
you've been more than enough for me to handle.

733
00:39:32,710 --> 00:39:34,840
How could I possibly have the energy for anyone else?

734
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:36,870
So he is...

735
00:39:36,870 --> 00:39:38,120
the Crown Prince?

736
00:39:39,230 --> 00:39:40,040
Call him Senior Brother.

737
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:46,490
[The Crown Prince]

738
00:39:56,430 --> 00:39:57,470
The old man is dead.

739
00:39:57,840 --> 00:39:59,190
I cannot let this grudge go unanswered.

740
00:40:01,190 --> 00:40:02,230
Please, Your Highness, grant me this.

741
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,080
Rise.

742
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:11,190
Do you think I haven't thought of avenging our teacher?

743
00:40:12,520 --> 00:40:14,040
If it weren't for my pleas,

744
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:16,360
he wouldn't have met this end.

745
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:18,520
But now,

746
00:40:19,120 --> 00:40:20,190
the court is in chaos.

747
00:40:20,800 --> 00:40:22,840
The Military Commissioner is holding his own army.

748
00:40:23,670 --> 00:40:25,870
And Yizhou is not even under my jurisdiction.

749
00:40:26,230 --> 00:40:27,320
Our teacher's death

750
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:30,190
may be a warning to me.

751
00:40:31,630 --> 00:40:33,390
If Your Highness give me the chance,

752
00:40:34,910 --> 00:40:35,710
Yizhou

753
00:40:37,280 --> 00:40:39,230
can forever remain the Emperor's Yizhou.

754
00:40:40,600 --> 00:40:42,000
You want to help me break this deadlock?

755
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:45,230
So,

756
00:40:45,390 --> 00:40:47,470
you're not only the Crown Prince's subordinate

757
00:40:47,470 --> 00:40:48,840
but also his junior brother.

758
00:40:51,230 --> 00:40:54,040
And Yizhou's fate is tied to the standing of Chang'an?

759
00:40:54,870 --> 00:40:56,000
That depends

760
00:40:56,390 --> 00:40:57,800
on what I can uncover.

761
00:40:58,600 --> 00:40:59,600
How do you plan to investigate?

762
00:41:00,670 --> 00:41:02,630
Niu Jin knows my identity now.

763
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:05,280
He'll undoubtedly be more cautious in the future.

764
00:41:05,630 --> 00:41:06,840
But his past deeds

765
00:41:07,040 --> 00:41:08,430
would leave traces.

766
00:41:09,230 --> 00:41:10,600
Now that he knows

767
00:41:10,870 --> 00:41:12,120
I've looked into Nanzhao,

768
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:13,710
he wouldn't dare

769
00:41:13,710 --> 00:41:16,080
to tamper with anyone tied to that line

770
00:41:16,230 --> 00:41:17,280
for fear of exposing himself.

771
00:41:18,190 --> 00:41:20,000
Niu Jin produces the Shu brocade,

772
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,470
Nanzhao buys the Shu brocade,

773
00:41:23,390 --> 00:41:25,390
so who transports

774
00:41:25,710 --> 00:41:26,670
the brocade?

775
00:41:30,080 --> 00:41:32,630
From Yizhou to Nanzhao,

776
00:41:32,630 --> 00:41:33,800
