777
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:35,630
To avoid detection,

778
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:37,390
one must disguise themselves.

779
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:39,600
You want to investigate foreign merchants?

780
00:41:41,630 --> 00:41:42,430
You're smart!

781
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:45,760
But with so many foreign merchants,

782
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:46,870
