783
00:41:51,600 --> 00:41:52,800
I have someone in mind.

784
00:41:53,950 --> 00:41:55,390
I've thought of someone too.

785
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:57,120
- Bai Sheng! - Prince Bai of Nanzhao!

786
00:41:58,150 --> 00:41:59,000
Prince Bai?

787
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:03,800
Sheng Fengze.

788
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:08,230
Sheng Fengze...

789
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:12,950
Bai Sheng...

790
00:42:14,710 --> 00:42:16,870
Could they be the same person?

791
00:42:19,190 --> 00:42:20,230
It's possible.

792
00:42:25,360 --> 00:42:26,560
But based on his age,

793
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:28,000
he would have been just a child

794
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:30,000
