795
00:42:30,560 --> 00:42:31,670
That doesn't add up.

796
00:42:32,670 --> 00:42:35,190
However, if he's only involved in smuggling,

797
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:38,630
why would he personally travel such great distances to Yizhou?

798
00:42:39,950 --> 00:42:41,280
And later, when he approached me,

799
00:42:41,950 --> 00:42:43,190
